snippet.title: Elio: A Fantasie of Light and Darkness
snippet.description:
Expand your town, customize your party with over 200 classes and charge into dungeons!
Elio: A Fantasie of Light and Darkness is now available for Android!

Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=kemco.hitpoint.seisen&hl=en

Ruleria, a world created by the gods. As the God of the Sun, you awaken in order to face wicked monsters that have suddenly appeared out of nowhere...
Expand your town, form your forces with over 200 classes, and customize the character looks with endless combinations! 

©2015 KEMCO/Hit-Point
※All graphics terms, characters and elements are subject to change in the actual product.
